                          </li>
                          
                        </ul>
                      </div>
                    </li>
                  </ul>
          
        
    
        
        
        
        
        
          
        
    
  </ul>
</nav>
    
  
</div>
        <div class="site-content__content">
          <main id="main-content" class="site-l-content-wrapper--styleguide large-screen:vads-u-margin-top--neg2">
            
              
              
                <div>
  <p class="site-content__section-name">
    Foundation
  </p>
</div>
              
            
            <h1 id="flexbox">Flexbox</h1>

<div class="va-introtext">
  <p>The flexbox utilities provide all of the properties for flex containers and some for flex items. All are responsive. Read about <a href="#responsive-prefixes">responsive prefixes</a>. This utility can serve as compliment to the <a href="../layout/flexbox-grid">flexbox grid</a>.</p>
</div>

<p>Flexbox requires two components,  a <em>flex container</em> and <em>flex items</em>. Any first siblings in a flex container becomes a flex item. It is not possible for any of those siblings to not become a flex item.</p>

<nav aria-labelledby="on-this-page" class="site-on-this-page">
  <dl class="site-on-this-page__list">
    <dt id="on-this-page" role="heading" aria-level="2" class="site-on-this-page__title">
      On this page
    </dt>
  
    <dd role="definition" class="site-on-this-page__definition">
      <a class="site-on-this-page__link" href="#flex">
        <i aria-hidden="true" class="fas fa-arrow-down"></i>
        Flex
      </a>
    </dd>
  
    <dd role="definition" class="site-on-this-page__definition">
      <a class="site-on-this-page__link" href="#flex-direction">
        <i aria-hidden="true" class="fas fa-arrow-down"></i>
        Flex direction
      </a>
    </dd>
  
    <dd role="definition" class="site-on-this-page__definition">
      <a class="site-on-this-page__link" href="#flex-wrap">
        <i aria-hidden="true" class="fas fa-arrow-down"></i>
        Flex wrap
      </a>
    </dd>
  
    <dd role="definition" class="site-on-this-page__definition">
      <a class="site-on-this-page__link" href="#align-items">
